'''Arví''' is the second and last station on line L of the [[Medellín Metro]]. It is located in the Santa Elena village of [[Medellín]].<ref name="A.2007">{{cite book|author=José Ángel Báez A.|title=El poder paisa: Antioquia y Medellín en acción|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=iu4SAQAAIAAJ|date=2007|publisher=Semana|via=Google Books}}</ref> It was inaugurated in early 2010, along with [[Arví park]], which caters to tourists. It uses the same [[Metrocable (Medellín)|metrocable system]] as lines J and K.

